data.description: Spacious living & dining rooms with new carpet & vinyl planks.  Recently remodeled,  spacious kitchen.  Recently remodeled first floor laundry within bonus room (potential home office).  Remodeled full & half baths. Newer plumbing throughout.  Household electric upgraded. Newer windows & interior doors. New front door 2015. Vinyl privacy fenced backyard. 12x10 newer shed.  Full width front porch refresh with composite steps added 2015. High efficiency furnace installed 2011. New water heater 2014.
data.whatILove: Loads of classic character with lofty 9'ceilings on the main level. Abundant, smart storage additions. Completely refreshed interior with modern amenities make for a wonderful home.
